dct_title_s: Bus Routes and Stops Waukesha, Wisconsin 2008
dct_description_sm: The point data layer represents bus stops for the City of Waukesha, Wisconsin in 2008. The line data layers represent various bus routes for the City of Waukesha, Wisconsin in 2008. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Waukesha_Bus_2008.gdb. The dataset was originally published by the City of Waukesha Public Works Department-GIS Division in 2008.
